  "comment": "Atomic Pro Rudy Moving Head BSW 200W: The Atomic Pro Rudy 3in1 is a moving head with variable optics able to work in beam and spot mode, as well as the wash effect using the zoom in combination with the frost filter. Equipped with two gobo wheels, one with static gobos and one with interchangeable rotating gobos, it offers a 4-sided prism. The light source is 200W Led, the machine is equipped with electronic focus and mechanical dimmer",
